etwork requests from your environment: provide the zip (or each HTML file) as downloadable output named <batch>-sites.zip instead, and say so. IMPORTANT: ignore image_url fields entirely \u2014 do not fetch them; design from palette + ad_text. ad_text is raw OCR and may contain typos: use it to identify services only, never copy garbled text verbatim. If an email looks inconsistent with the business name, omit it.",
